data.name: INFUSION PUMP SYRINGES
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Barrel + Plunger: Medical Grade Polypropylene (PP)
- Gasket: Isoprene Latex-Free Rubber and Natural Rubber

## STERILIZATION

## PRESENTATIONS
- Luer Lock and Luer Slip Tips
- With and Without Needle
- Latex and latex-free Gasket
- Customizable graduation including logo

## PERFORMANCE
- Clear graduation printing technology
- High Transparency and UV-Light Proof colour Barrel
- Fit ALL-STANDARD pumps brands worldwide
- Smooth sliding
- Smooth Surface

## ANESTHESIA
